  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidSequenceException
    An error to be thrown if a passed password contains more than 2 of the same character in a row.
    LengthException
    An error to be thrown if the length of a password is less than 6 characters long.
    NoDigitException
    An error to be thrown if a password does not contain a numeric digit.
    NoLowerAlphaException
    An error to be thrown if a password does not contain a lowercase character.
    NoUpperAlphaException
    An error to be thrown if a password does not contain an uppercase letter.
    UnmatchedException
    An error to be thrown if a password typed and a retyped password do not match.
